sentences.sentence: And where my brother set the laburnum on his birth-day.
sentences.translation: 我弟弟在他生日那天将金链花种在它旁边。

sentences.sentence: My address is No 22 Laburnum Close so his must be No 26.
sentences.translation: 我的地址是拉布耐姆巷22号，所以他的地址一定是26号。
